article.description: — Money Williams scored 21 points as Montana beat San Jose State 75-58 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Williams scores 25, Montana defeats San Jose State 75-58
article.linkText: Williams scores 25, Montana defeats San Jose State 75-58
article.story: MISSOULA, Mont. -- — Money Williams scored 21 points as Montana beat San Jose State 75-58 on Saturday night. Williams added nine rebounds for the Grizzlies (3-4). Te'Jon Sawyer scored 17 points, shooting 8 of 10 from the field. Josh Vazquez shot 3 for 5 from beyond the arc to finish with nine points. William Humer led the Spartans (5-4) in scoring, finishing with 11 points. Alvaro Cardenas Torre added nine points and five assists for San Jose State. Latrell Davis also recorded nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
